data.title: Widow of John Sherwood, Skier Who Died at Breck, Sues Teen Over Fatal Collision
meta_keywords: Waterville Valley Academy Black and Blue Trail Smashers
data.meta_description: The widow of a New Jersey man who died in a fatal collision at Breckenridge has filed a lawsuit naming the teen who collided with him and others as defendants. Get the story at Westword.com.
